{"tid":1467314,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"永遠不割，但需冷靜思考！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:12.000Z","uid":71924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7916bcd582cc7c502bb9c0f57b1bf2310b2043e4","tid":1467314,"uid":71924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:40.000Z","msg":"根本政府一d都唔驚勇武，最想煽動你地，捉撚晒你班人就最好。<br />\n<br />\n佢地而家最驚既係覺醒左既和理非呀！<br />\n點解呀？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">和理非今次全面覺醒，無人再想要袋住先</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">個個都非五大訴求不可。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n琴日一轉機場，玩撚到個政府on99<br />\n佢地最驚和理非，點解呀<br />\n因為和理非最驚比人拉<br />\n一定唔會搞事<br />\n唔搞事，d犬點出動呀？<br />\n出動唔到，日日搞鳩你，搞到你日日取消、延誤航班，可以點樣唔跪呀？點冷處理都無辦法忽略到個損失呀。d報紙話搞香港機場仲衰過中美貿易戰！<br />\n<br />\n今晚好爆，捉到公安，我理撚得佢鬼唔鬼，只要有一樣野捉起到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恐共情緒</span></span>，（你估左報講既野流架，佢地都最撚驚呢樣搞到全民覺醒呀！）原來係證據確鑿，未覺醒個500萬都分分鐘開始驚，有乜勁過呢個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">核彈</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">係機場個到，淡淡定</span></span>，捉到既綁住佢，佢唔覺意跌左證件就「執返比佢」比記者問佢地，記者覺得夠爆記自然會報啦！唔洗咁緊張激動！<br />\n<br />\n要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冷靜，發現到咩都要冷靜。</span></span><br />\n邊個係咁講埋晒d打7佢既，就拉拉個位小姐/人兄，唔好比佢係中心位置。<br />\n<br />\n唔係割呀，係驚咁搞法，機場都入唔撚到呀<br />\n自己白白洗失機會。<br />\n手握覺醒和理非+冷靜勇武，我地真係唔會輸架！！<br />\n<br />\n唔好比運動失焦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尚未成功，仍需努力<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日打人個d一定係狗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"be2e99c1af3b8945d27400b98d713fbef2e0f514","tid":1467314,"uid":71924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2613009d8d6639d871f61298b69c984b3db37849","tid":1467314,"uid":71924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:20.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"a311b9324614e34e52a4be099de87c9b1319ca93","tid":1467314,"uid":71924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:17.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"5e1588fcb1d2da269047be12ad6a7af50cdc98a0","tid":1467314,"uid":71924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"3d8a0124974a29bdd74f8a4a2e20dc08ede0b72e","tid":1467314,"uid":71924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:12.000Z","msg":"推"}]}